WEBVTT

00:00:00.437 --> 00:00:02.675
Adam Grant: When I was just
starting my career,

00:00:02.699 --> 00:00:05.770
I knew that to one day get tenure,
I had to be productive.

00:00:05.794 --> 00:00:07.492
Publish or perish.

00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:09.882
So, early in grad school,

00:00:09.906 --> 00:00:12.598
I started submitting
research papers to top journals.

00:00:12.974 --> 00:00:15.076
The first one got rejected.

00:00:15.628 --> 00:00:16.828
So did the second.

00:00:17.165 --> 00:00:21.035
Experts in my own field were telling me
that my work was not good enough.

00:00:21.610 --> 00:00:23.491
I wondered if I should drop out.

00:00:23.974 --> 00:00:27.814
I'd been working on a third paper,
so I decided to give it one more shot.

00:00:28.331 --> 00:00:30.195
I spent months perfecting it,